other.name: :question: Other Category
other.desc: A category with commands that don't belong in other categories. You can type `.help <command>` to get some more detailed info on a command!

image.name: :camera: Image Category
image.desc: A command category consisting of image manipulation commands. You can type `.help <command>` to get some more detailed info on a command!

moderation.name: :hammer: Moderation Category
moderation.desc: A command category consisting of moderation related commands. You can type `.help <command>` to get some more detailed info on a command!

missionpassed.name: Mission Passed
missionpassed.desc: Adds a mission passed overlay to your profile picture

wasted.name: Wasted
wasted.desc: Adds a wasted text to a mentioned user's profile picture.

simpcard.name: Simpcard
simpcard.desc: Creates a simpcard for the given user.

ironic.name: Ironic
ironic.desc: Sends your message but with randomly generated capital letters.

clear.name: Clear
clear.desc: Deletes a given amount of messages!

lockdown.name: Lockdown
lockdown.desc: A command used to lock a channel (make people unable to type).

help.name: Help
help.desc: Sends you info on a given command.

eject.name: Eject
eject.desc: Generates an Among Us like ejected screen.

hug.name: Hug
hug.desc: A command that lets you hug someone!

triggered.name: Triggered
triggered.desc: Sends a triggered version of your profile picture.
